Name: Therapist
Text: So he made it all out, just by hiding behind the bushes and trees?

Name: Bieda
Text: Yes... I feel ashamed, However, I was a little bit sleepy. Yes yes.

Name: Bieda
Text: The next day, I hid his gold again but, I started looking behind the obstacles.

Name: Bieda
Text: You know, I can pass through objects.

Name: Therapist
Text: How did it go? Tell me about it.
